      "content": "That feeling of being inconsequential is a painful kind of loneliness, and it's completely understandable why you'd feel that way when the connections feel so shallow. Please know that your internal experience is real, regardless of how others perceive it online. If these feelings of worthlessness become overwhelming, reaching out to a professional can provide a space where your voice is truly heard and valued. There are people who want to listen to what you're going through.",
      "source": "target",
